00:44:58,820 --> 00:45:01,220
 he became the first leader of our church,

1101
00:45:01,220 --> 00:45:04,060
 one of the greatest leaders our church has ever known.

1102
00:45:04,060 --> 00:45:07,180
 And that's what God is calling you today.

