 past 401ks and W2s, God has a bigger vision for your work.

1108
00:45:28,540 --> 00:45:33,060
 Your work is a vehicle that the gospel moves forward on.

1109
00:45:33,060 --> 00:45:35,220
 It always has been.

1110
00:45:35,220 --> 00:45:38,060
 The gospel moves into countries and into new places

1111
00:45:38,060 --> 00:45:40,340
 and everywhere through our work.

