00:47:41,700 --> 00:47:42,540
 "It's more money.

1168
00:47:42,540 --> 00:47:43,460
 "It's more flexibility.

1169
00:47:43,460 --> 00:47:44,980
 "You're more passionate about it.

1170
00:47:44,980 --> 00:47:47,300
 "It's getting to work with a buddy.

1171
00:47:47,300 --> 00:47:49,460
 "This is a no brainer, done deal.

