00:48:35,580 --> 00:48:39,140
 "I don't know that the Lord has opened this door to me.

1192
00:48:39,140 --> 00:48:41,260
 "It's not clear and I don't know that he's living out

1193
00:48:41,260 --> 00:48:43,480
 "his purpose at his current job."

